snippet.title: Asfalia Fear - Out Now - Trailer
snippet.description:
Get the game now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2436410/Asfalia_Fear/

Adventure awaits you in this colorful, family-friendly point-and-click delight! Navigate through a world painted with emotions, where even 'fear' becomes a playful friend. Solve puzzles, collect stickers, and share giggles in a heartwarming journey in the world of emotions.
